    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161930/extras/958f262a0a7aef3a96f9dbaa387c6585.poster.avif?t=1760039823\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161930/extras/958f262a0a7aef3a96f9dbaa387c6585.webm?t=1760039823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161930/extras/958f262a0a7aef3a96f9dbaa387c6585.mp4?t=1760039823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Duck Norris Tales is pixel run and gun action game heavily focused on boss battles. Featuring highly stylized pixel art inspired by the arcade games from the '90s.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>Step into the feathers of a brave duck on a mission of revenge after aliens destroy his favorite ice cream shop! Join him on an epic journey through the depths of the Earth as he uncovers secrets, battles monsters, and rallies the Gods to aid in his quest. Can he save humanity along the way?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE BATTLE</h2>The Gods are divided and at war, and it's up to you to restore peace and earn their respect. Each time you challenge a God, you have the chance to gain their blessing and grow stronger! Learn new abilities and make new allies to unlock powerful super moves as you strive to bring balance.<br><br>Uncover secrets about the world and unlock devastating super attacks as you cleanse the land.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161930/extras/550f6d3fc9c98a5935ca21188d7547e8.avif?t=1760039823\" width=640 height=360 /></span>",
